# WPA2-PSK 4-way EAPOL handshake (owfuzz as STA/supplicant fuzzing the AP/authenticator of VIVOFIBRA-WIFI6-CF81) flow — generated by spec_reader from spec text.
# owfuzz drives these states (NOT hardcoded in its C); frames come from the -p corpus
# by @send id. on_rx 'TYPE match=OFF:HH' = a received TYPE frame whose byte at offset OFF
# (from frame start, MAC header included) == 0xHH.
#
# in_state    | on_rx            | send        | goto_state
INIT          | START            | auth_open   | WAIT_AUTH
WAIT_AUTH     | AUTH             | assoc_req   | WAIT_ASSOC
WAIT_ASSOC    | ASSOCRES         | -           | WAIT_M1
WAIT_M1       | QOSDATA match=40:8a | m2          | WAIT_M3
WAIT_M3       | QOSDATA match=40:ca | m4          | DONE
